Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:40.48,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,あの、実は練習時間のことだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:44.80,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:45.78,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,それで…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:47.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,そう言われても困るわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:53.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:55.84,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,それは分かっているんだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.33,Default,Takahashi,0,0,0,,皆が…
